page.title: 16DAY IN THE LIFE 2
page.content: AT 7 0 CLOCK I WOKE UP AND GOT WASHED WENT DOWNSTAIRS AND HAD MY BREAKFAST ,BRUSHED MY HAIR AND BRUSHED MY TEETH THEN I PUT MY COAT ON. WENT TO SCHOOL. WHEN I GOT TO SCHOOL I PLAYED OUTSIDE UNTIL THE BELL RUNG.WHEN IT HAD RUNG I WENT INTO CLASS AND SAID MY PRAYERS AND SAT DOWN.I DID S.M.P.(SCHOOL MATHEMATICS PROJECT) UNTIL FIRST BREAK , THEN I COULD CARRY ON DOING S.M.P.OR I COULD DO 9 A DAY. I DID THAT UNTIL DINNER BREAK.AFTER I HAD HAD MY DINNER I CAME IN TO DO SOME LANGUAGE PATTERNS UNTIL 3.00, AND THEN I READ A BOOK UNTIL 3.30 AND WENT HOME.WHEN I GOT HOME I WASHED MY HAIR AND WATCHED TELEVISION AFTER THAT I DID MY HOMEWORK AND HAD MY TEA.
